snippet.textDisplay: It is truly disheartening to witness the desecration of legendary music. Arnob, it is evident that you have yet to produce anything truly unique. Instead, you have resorted to dismantling the creations of others. Your actions are not a form of music, nor are they a fusion of any kind. Rather, they resemble nothing more than random dots on the street. It is a shame that you and your team have chosen to engage in such behavior.

snippet.textDisplay:
Diversity in its picks. No one can replace Pritam Bhai's magical creativity. The next day is the birthday of our very own Kabiguru and today Pritam has blessed us with this soulful composition of our own culture. As a boy belong to the riverside Haor area, I can relate to this song with much nostalgia and love.
Palakar's high voice reflects the culture of Haor, where everyone has to sing in such a way that everyone connects the rhythm with the sound of the boat.

Love to Pritom bhai and Team. Hail haor culture.
